TextEng: What? I ain't following nobody... just... uh... strolling. Yeah, that's it.
Text: 뭐? 난 아무도 안 따라다녀... 그냥... 어... 산책 중이야. 그래, 그거야.

TextEng: Oh, no problem. Don't you worry. I'll just be on my way then. Yes, on my way... Nice stuff you got there...
Text: 아, 문제없어. 걱정 마. 그럼 갈게. 그래, 가는 거야... 좋은 물건 갖고 있네...

TextEng: I wasn't... I didn't mean... Blast it! I'll never make the gold at this rate!
Text: 난 안... 그런 뜻이... 젠장! 이러다간 절대 돈을 못 모아!

TextEng: Look, I don't want any trouble. I was just looking for an easy mark. Obviously that ain't you, so I'll just be going.
Text: 이봐, 문제 일으키기 싫어. 그냥 쉬운 호구를 찾고 있었어. 분명히 넌 아니니까 그냥 갈게.

TextEng: You know about that? Nobody's supposed to know. Everybody does though. Like it was leaked out or something.
Text: 그거 알아? 아무도 모르는 거였는데. 근데 다들 알더라. 누가 흘린 것 같아.

TextEng: I don't know, I just heard that a plague cure was coming up for auction in the Seedy Tavern. Just let me get back to work...
Text: 몰라, 그냥 시디 선술집에서 역병 치료제가 경매에 나온다고 들었어. 그냥 일하러 가게 해줘...

TextEng: I'll never be able to afford it at this rate. Could steal the whole district and not have enough, I bet.
Text: 이러다간 절대 못 사. 지구 전체를 털어도 부족할 거야, 장담해.

TextEng: Just trying to stay alive! Just trying!
Text: 그냥 살아남으려고! 그냥!

TextEng: Who, me? I don't know much about it. It's at the Seedy Tavern. It's funded by Bloodsailors... that means Vengaul is involved somehow.
Text: 나? 그것에 대해 잘 몰라. 시디 선술집에서 해. 핏빛 항해자들이 후원하는 거야... 그러니까 벵골이 뭔가 관련됐다는 거지.

TextEng: I ain't doing nothing, friend. Just sitting on the corner...
Text: 아무것도 안 해, 친구. 그냥 모퉁이에 앉아있을 뿐...

TextEng: Don't have one. Nope. Just some nameless guy on the corner. Nothing to get concerned about...
Text: 없어. 응. 그냥 모퉁이의 이름 없는 녀석이야. 신경 쓸 거 없어...

TextEng: Don't know anything about anything... just standing on a corner.
Text: 아무것도 몰라... 그냥 모퉁이에 서 있을 뿐이야.

TextEng: Just you move along, hmm... I ain't got time for paupers... I need some high rollers...
Text: 그냥 가, 흠... 거지한테 쓸 시간 없어... 큰손이 필요해...

TextEng: You should, ah, be careful with that gear of yours... looks expensive... worth a bit... yeah.
Text: 그, 어, 그 장비 조심해야겠네... 비싸 보여... 꽤 나가겠어... 응.

TextEng: Gotta wait for the moment... should I... they look pretty tough... I don't know...
Text: 때를 기다려야 해... 할까... 꽤 강해 보이는데... 모르겠어...

TextEng: That's a fine looking weapon there... worth a lot, I bet... better keep an eye on it.
Text: 좋은 무기 갖고 있네... 비쌀 거야, 장담해... 잘 지켜야 할 거야.

TextEng: Evening... mighty fine gear you have there... got to be worth a pretty penny, I imagine...
Text: 안녕... 좋은 장비 갖고 있네... 꽤 나가겠지, 아마...

TextEng: Get along, you pauper... gotta find someone with the stuff... expensive stuff...
Text: 저리 가, 거지야... 물건 있는 놈을 찾아야지... 비싼 물건...

TextEng: Gotta find a mark... come to daddy...
Text: 호구를 찾아야지... 이리 와라...

TextEng: Here, I'll give you my copy of the notice. I can't afford to go anyway. Just don't hurt me.
Text: 여기, 내가 가진 안내문 줄게. 어차피 갈 돈도 없어. 그냥 때리지 마.

TextEng: What? I never... I mean... aw, I'm sorry. I just gotta get some gold together... I wasn't going to do anything to you.
Text: 뭐? 난 절대... 그러니까... 아, 미안해. 그냥 돈을 좀 모아야 해서... 너한테 뭔가 하려던 건 아니야.

TextEng: Nothing anyone else couldn't tell you. It's in the north central of the district, and it's where the black market usually is.
Text: 다른 사람도 말해줄 수 있는 거야. 지구 북쪽 중앙에 있고, 보통 암시장이 있는 곳이야.

TextEng: Well, anyone that stays around here for long hears about Vengaul Bloodsail. He's flashy, and he likes showing off. The bloodsailors are his... pirates, mostly.
Text: 뭐, 여기 오래 있는 사람은 다 벵골 블러드세일에 대해 들어. 화려하고 과시하기 좋아해. 핏빛 항해자들은 그의 부하야... 대부분 해적.

TextEng: A guy like me can't even get in there. They've got a brick wall of a bouncer that won't let anyone in that isn't a Bloodsailor.
Text: 나 같은 놈은 거기 들어갈 수도 없어. 핏빛 항해자가 아니면 아무도 안 들여보내는 벽돌 같은 문지기가 있거든.

TextEng: Them uniforms is hard to come by. Of course, maybe if I got enough gold together, she might say different. I don't know.
Text: 그 유니폼은 구하기 어려워. 물론 돈을 충분히 모으면 다르게 말할지도 몰라. 모르겠어.

TextEng: Well, it's a big group. One guy can't run the whole thing. Vengaul, he's a showman, but he needs some organizers too.
Text: 뭐, 큰 조직이잖아. 한 사람이 다 운영할 수 없어. 벵골은 쇼맨이지만 조직하는 사람도 필요해.

TextEng: I hear that his first lieutenant is hot under the collar right now. Callik's his name... but I ain't saying anything else... I don't know anything else.
Text: 그의 부관이 지금 화가 나 있다고 들었어. 칼릭이라고... 하지만 더는 말 안 해... 더는 몰라.
